title: Lunchbox Reveals His List of Top 25 Most Famous People in Country Music + Spin the Wheel: Guy Who Has To Wear Lace Boxers + Bobby Feud: Most Used Words in Country Music
itunes:title: Lunchbox Reveals His List of Top 25 Most Famous People in Country Music + Spin the Wheel: Guy Who Has To Wear Lace Boxers + Bobby Feud: Most Used Words in Country Music
description:
Bobby lets Lunchbox read his list of who he thinks are the Top 25 most famous people in country music and where he ranks himself. We spin the wheel and the loser has to wear a pair of lace boxers that were in the news. We also played a round of the Bobby Feud to see if you can guess the most commonly used songs in country music. Bobby talks to a listener who was calling to fact check us on a segment that leads into how she has given birth 4 times in her home…in her own bed…and why she decided to do it.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
